OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778609470
OL,3,CBelfast restaurant window smashed
OL,4,Cduring youth disorder
OL,6,FTwo fast food restaurants in east
OL,7,FBelfast closed on Saturday because of
OL,8,Fdisorder caused by large groups of
OL,9,Fyoung people, the PSNI said.
OL,11,FOne of the restaurants in the
OL,12,FConnswater area had a window smashed
OL,13,Fand the force has asked parents to
OL,14,Fspeak to their children so they do not
OL,15,Fget involved in dangerous behaviour.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
