OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778609470
OL,3,CBelfast restaurant window smashed
OL,4,Cduring youth disorder
OL,6,FIn a statement, the PSNI said a
OL,7,Fplanned parade in the Newtownards Road
OL,8,Farea of east Belfast largely passed
OL,9,Foff peacefully but that they had
OL,10,Freceived a number of reports of anti-
OL,11,Fsocial behaviour and altercations
OL,12,Faround the event.
OL,14,FChief Inspector Robinson said: "A
OL,15,Fnumber of reports were received around
OL,16,Fthe parade, which largely passed off
OL,17,Fpeacefully, of anti-social behaviour
OL,18,Fand altercations.
OL,26,@vD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
