PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778609470
OL,3,CBelfast restaurant window smashed
OL,4,Cduring youth disorder
OL,6,F"Two fast food restaurants in the
OL,7,FConnswater area had to close after
OL,8,Flarge groups of young people gathered
OL,9,Fin the area, engaged in disorderly
OL,10,Fbehaviour and smashed one of the
OL,11,Fwindows.
OL,13,F"Officers attended and dispersed the
OL,14,Fcrowds, and remained in the area for a
OL,15,Ftime to ensure calm."
OL,17,FPolice were investigating the
OL,18,Fincidents and gathering evidence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@UO]
