CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778609470
OL,3,CBelfast restaurant window smashed
OL,4,Cduring youth disorder
OL,6,FMr Robinson said "there will be
OL,7,Fconsequences" for those involved in
OL,8,Foffending.
OL,10,FHe said: "We would particularly ask
OL,11,Fparents and guardians to speak to
OL,12,Ftheir children so they know where they
OL,13,Fare, and to play their part in
OL,14,Fensuring that they do not become
OL,15,Finvolved in such reckless behaviour
OL,16,Fthat could lead to someone getting
OL,17,Fhurt."
OL,26,@nD@ROUoD@MO]rD@JOUyD@FO]
